blog.description: Update Once or twice (reblog stuff that contains my artwork! or art stuff mentioning me)I’m Sonia, 21, open for requests! I don’t care if your blog is non-art related or filled with inappropriate content, but you are welcome to view my art and follow me if you like! My art is trash and you’re not welcome to repost my art as yours! Send me ideas on what you want me to draw. (If you want Nsfm, you gotta have the dough to make me do it!)Only friends can get my art by commissions(chip in on PayPal!) -paypal.me/pools/c/86TRH8qE0E -Search for show and au names listed below⬇️-Hotel Inu(Inuyasha crossover)- Anime espionage(another crossover)- Multidimensional Surge(Yokai watch/Bakugan AU crossover) - MS: Shadow Planet (In progress) -Semester at Space!(mini crossover and same stuff). Check me out on Twitter: @Bearlycute64 https://www.paypal.me/Bearlycuteart
